We laugh with all our hearts we love with all our hearts… we literally inspire the world to be vulnerable. This photo represents more then a picture .. it represents strength & vulnerability in me & everyone. Photos are supposed to speak to you. That’s why we live in a world where images take control more then what we write. Yin Yoga and Reiki Fusion anyone?

Join us for a deeply nourishing and relaxing experience in our Yin Yoga and Reiki Fusion class with @KatieKepronFitness, @un.soin.avec.charlotte, @sun.healinggoddexx and @alexrobshaw.

This offering combines the gentle yet profound practice of Yin Yoga with the healing energy of Reiki, creating a harmonious blend that promotes relaxation, balance, and inner peace.

The combination of Yin Yoga and Reiki creates a profound synergy, releasing energetic blockages, enhancing the benefits of both practices and facilitating a deeper connection to yourself.

Whether you are a beginner or an experienced yogi, this class is suitable for all levels. Come and join us as we explore the harmonious union of Yin Yoga and Reiki, allowing you to cultivate a sense of deep relaxation, renewal, and energetic harmony.

🎟 Tickets on sale now! Link in bio. 

____________________________________

Yin Yoga et Reiki Fusion, ça vous dit ?

Rejoignez-nous pour une expérience profondément nourrissante et relaxante dans notre cours de Yin Yoga et Reiki Fusion.

Ce cours combine la pratique douce et profonde du Yin Yoga avec l’énergie curative du Reiki, créant ainsi un mélange harmonieux qui favorise la relaxation, l’équilibre et la paix intérieure.

La combinaison du Yin Yoga et du Reiki crée une profonde synergie, libérant les blocages énergétiques, augmentant les bénéfices des deux pratiques et facilitant une connexion plus profonde avec soi-même.

Que vous soyez débutant ou expérimenté, ce cours est adapté à tous les niveaux. Venez nous rejoindre pour explorer l’union harmonieuse du Yin Yoga et du Reiki, vous permettant de cultiver un sentiment de relaxation profonde, de renouveau et d’harmonie énergétique.

This year has been an absolute journey for me on so many large levels that it would be hard to describe it in a post. And for now I’ll keep the details to myself … but I have to say not only do I recognize the growth in me… but when I doubt myself I really have given my inner monologue a change of pace. Honour & gratitude 🙏 have been some big words that sit true very deep within now. 

As my birthday creeps in it’s given me a lot to reflect on 📚 

Here is a little poolside dip.. & me staring all my challenges and fears right in the face. Saying I “see you… and baby we got this” believe in yourself…that’s the most important powerful journey of them all ☺️🍯
